main event: Two circular white objects were sighted by the flight engineer on an American Airlines commercial airliner on 8 November 1964.
interesting points: The objects were estimated to be 30-40 feet in diameter., The objects exhibited high-speed movements and hovered at times., The sighting occurred at an altitude of about 20,000 feet., The captain and first officer also confirmed the sighting., There were no obvious navigation or running lights visible on the objects.
witness description: flight engineer, captain, and first officer on an American Airlines commercial airliner
